'''索科特拉省'''（{{lang-ar|أرخبيل سقطرى}}，{{transl|ar|ʾArḫabīl Suquṭrā}}）是[[也门|也门]]的一个[[也门行政区划|省]]，管辖[[索科特拉群岛|索科特拉群岛]]。

==历史==
从英国早期殖民开始，索科特拉就成为了{{le|迈赫拉苏丹国|Mahra Sultanate}}的一部分，后来成为[[亚丁保护国|亚丁保护国]]的一部分。1967年随[[南也门|南也门]]一同独立，虽然距离很远，但是依然由[[亚丁省|亚丁省]]管辖。2004年划归[[哈德拉毛省|哈德拉毛省]]管辖<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.yementimes.com/en/1724/report/3058/Independent-Socotra-governorate-paving-the-way-for-a-federal-Yemen-or-a-hint-at-separation.htm|agency=Yemen Times|title=INDEPENDENT SOCOTRA GOVERNORATE: PAVING THE WAY FOR A FEDERAL YEMEN OR A HINT AT SEPARATION?|first=Ali|last=Abulohoom|date=2013-10-29|accessdate=2015-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414093721/http://www.yementimes.com/en/1724/report/3058/Independent-Socotra-governorate-paving-the-way-for-a-federal-Yemen-or-a-hint-at-separation.htm|archive-date=2015-04-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2013年12月，索科特拉省成立，首府位于[[哈迪布|哈迪布]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sabanews.net/en/news353285.htm|title=Socotra, promising tourist site facing challenges|date=2014-05-14|accessdate=2015-04-10|first=Mohammad|last=Yaseen|agency=Saba News Agency|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611062612/http://www.sabanews.net/en/news353285.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年5月3日, 因於[[也门内战_(2015年至今)|也門內戰]]以致其政局不穩, [[阿聯酋|阿聯酋]]軍隊曾佔領該島, 並控制了島上機場和哈迪布。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/yemen-officials-say-emiratis-boost-forces-on-socotra-island/2018/05/02/84efa860-4e27-11e8-85c1-9326c4511033_story.html?utm_term=.31b060e05bdb|title=Yemen officials say Emiratis boost forces on Socotra island|website=The Washington Post|access-date=2018-05-07|archive-date=2018-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508121347/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/yemen-officials-say-emiratis-boost-forces-on-socotra-island/2018/05/02/84efa860-4e27-11e8-85c1-9326c4511033_story.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2018年4月30日，作为也门内战的一部分，阿拉伯联合酋长国部署了军队，并控制了[[索科特拉机场|索科特拉机场]]和海港。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/yemen-officials-say-emiratis-boost-forces-on-socotra-island/2018/05/02/84efa860-4e27-11e8-85c1-9326c4511033_story.html|title=Yemen officials say Emiratis boost forces on Socotra island|website=The Washington Post|access-date=2018-05-07|archive-date=2018-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180502195745/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/yemen-officials-say-emiratis-boost-forces-on-socotra-island/2018/05/02/84efa860-4e27-11e8-85c1-9326c4511033_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Socotra-How-a-strategic-island-became-part-of-a-Gulf-power-struggle-553599|title=SOCOTRA: HOW A STRATEGIC ISLAND BECAME PART OF A GULF POWER STRUGGLE|website=Jerusalem Post|access-date=2020-10-23|archive-date=2018-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180718042523/https://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Socotra-How-a-strategic-island-became-part-of-a-Gulf-power-struggle-553599|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2018年5月14日，沙特军队也部署在该岛，阿拉伯联合酋长国和也门之间促成了一项联合军事训练演习和将索科特拉机场和海港的行政控制权归还也门的协议。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/05/yemen-pm-crisis-uae-deployment-socotra-180514155240735.html|title=Yemen PM: Crisis over UAE deployment to Socotra over|website=Al Jazeera|access-date=2020-10-23|archive-date=2018-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180518212452/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/05/yemen-pm-crisis-uae-deployment-socotra-180514155240735.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.albawaba.com/news/yemen-uae-agree-deal-over-socotra-1131236|title=Yemen, UAE Agree on Deal Over Socotra|website=Albawaba News|access-date=2020-10-23|archive-date=2018-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516144222/https://www.albawaba.com/news/yemen-uae-agree-deal-over-socotra-1131236|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.presstv.com/Detail/2018/05/14/561645/Saudi-troops-Yemen-Socotra-UAE|title=Saudi Arabia deploys troops to Yemen’s Socotra after UAE’s military build-up|website=Press TV|access-date=2020-10-23|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125055504/http://www.presstv.com/Detail/2018/05/14/561645/Saudi-troops-Yemen-Socotra-UAE|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[南方过渡委员会|南方过渡委员会]]于2020年6月控制了该岛。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security-separatists/yemen-separatists-seize-remote-socotra-island-from-saudi-backed-government-idUSKBN23S0DU?il=0 |publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |date=June 21, 2020 |title=Yemen separatists seize remote Socotra island from Saudi-backed government |first=Mohammed |last=Mukhashaf |first2=Aziz |last2=El Yaakoubi |editor-first=Raissa |editor-last=Kasolowsky |quote=On Saturday, the STC announced it had seized government facilities and military bases on the main island of Socotra, a sparsely populated archipelago which sits at the mouth of the Gulf of Aden on one of the world’s busiest shipping lanes. |accessdate=2020-10-23 |archive-date=2021-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211121224115/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security-separatists/yemen-separatists-seize-remote-socotra-island-from-saudi-backed-government-idUSKBN23S0DU?il=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

